\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 ### Mission & Branding
\f1\b0 \cf4 \cb1 \strokec4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 CoachWillTumbles is an adventure-themed gymnastics coaching platform designed for parents booking private gymnastics lessons for their children. The brand emphasizes gymnastics as a "lifelong adventure" with quest-based terminology throughout the user experience.\cb1 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

