\cf5 \cb3 \strokec5 -\cf4 \strokec4  Skills presented as "Side Quests" (Flexibility, Strength, Agility, Meditation, Mental Blocks)\cb1 \
\cf5 \cb3 \strokec5 -\cf4 \strokec4  Blog renamed to "Adventure Stories"\cb1 \
\cf5 \cb3 \strokec5 -\cf4 \strokec4  Tips page called "Training Adventures"\cb1 \
\cf5 \cb3 \strokec5 -\cf4 \strokec4  Focus areas organized by apparatus with skill progression paths\cb1 \
