\cb3 ---\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ## 2. FRONTEND (React / Vite)\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Core Routing Structure\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Public Routes:**\cb1 \
\cb3 - `/` - Home page with hero, skills showcase, and adventure messaging\cb1 \
\cb3 - `/about` - Coach qualifications with gamified certification badges\cb1 \
\cb3 - `/booking` - Lesson booking with customer identification\cb1 \
\cb3 - `/blog` - Adventure Stories with filtering and search\cb1 \
\cb3 - `/blog/:id` - Individual blog post details\cb1 \
\cb3 - `/tips` - Training Adventures with difficulty levels\cb1 \
\cb3 - `/tips/:id` - Individual tip details with multi-section content\cb1 \
\cb3 - `/contact` - Contact information and FAQ\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Protected Routes:**\cb1 \
\cb3 - `/admin` - Admin dashboard (requires admin session)\cb1 \
\cb3 - `/admin/login` - Admin authentication\cb1 \
\cb3 - `/parent/login` - Parent email-code authentication\cb1 \
\cb3 - `/parent-dashboard` - Parent portal for managing bookings and athletes\cb1 \
\cb3 - `/booking-success` - Post-payment confirmation page\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Page Components & Data Flow\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Home Page (`/`)\cb1 \
\cb3 **Layout:**\cb1 \
\cb3 - Hero section with adventure-themed messaging\cb1 \
\cb3 - Skills showcase organized by apparatus (Vault, Bars, Beam, Floor)\cb1 \
\cb3 - Side Quests section featuring specialized training areas\cb1 \
\cb3 - Call-to-action sections with journey-focused language\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Data Fetched:**\cb1 \
\cb3 - `useQuery(['/api/stripe/products'])` - Live lesson pricing\cb1 \
\cb3 - No authentication required\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Key Interactions:**\cb1 \
\cb3 - "Start Their Journey" button triggers customer identification modal\cb1 \
\cb3 - Skill selection opens booking modal with pre-selected focus areas\cb1 \
\cb3 - Adventure theme throughout with non-transactional language\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Booking Page (`/booking`)\cb1 \
\cb3 **Layout:**\cb1 \
\cb3 - Lesson type cards with adventure names and descriptions\cb1 \
\cb3 - Customer identification modal for returning parents\cb1 \
\cb3 - Enhanced booking modal with multi-step wizard\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Data Fetched:**\cb1 \
\cb3 - `useQuery(['/api/stripe/products'])` - Lesson pricing\cb1 \
\cb3 - `useQuery(['/api/parent-auth/status'])` - Parent authentication status\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Main Interactions:**\cb1 \
\cb3 - Customer identification \uc0\u8594  BookingLoginModal \u8594  EnhancedBookingModal\cb1 \
\cb3 - Three booking flows: new-user, athlete-modal, parent-portal\cb1 \
\cb3 - Lesson selection with adventure-themed descriptions\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Parent Dashboard (`/parent-dashboard`)\cb1 \
\cb3 **Layout:**\cb1 \
\cb3 - Tab-based interface with elevated styling\cb1 \
\cb3 - Upcoming Sessions, Booking History, Athletes, Profile tabs\cb1 \
\cb3 - Mobile-optimized with 2-row grid layout\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Data Fetched:**\cb1 \
\cb3 - `useQuery(['/api/parent-auth/status'])` - Authentication status\cb1 \
\cb3 - `useQuery(['/api/parent/bookings'])` - Parent's booking history\cb1 \
\cb3 - `useQuery(['/api/parent/info'])` - Parent profile information\cb1 \
\cb3 - `useQuery(['/api/parent/athletes'])` - Associated athletes\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Key Features:**\cb1 \
\cb3 - Reschedule bookings with available time slots\cb1 \
\cb3 - Cancel bookings with refund policies\cb1 \
\cb3 - Edit athlete profiles with photo uploads\cb1 \
\cb3 - Update focus areas for future sessions\cb1 \
\cb3 - View waiver status and complete missing waivers\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Admin Dashboard (`/admin`)\cb1 \
\cb3 **Layout:**\cb1 \
\cb3 - 8 main tabs in responsive grid layout\cb1 \
\cb3 - Protected by `isAdminAuthenticated` middleware\cb1 \
\cb3 - Each tab has dedicated management components\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Data Fetched:**\cb1 \
\cb3 - `useQuery(['/api/auth/status'])` - Admin authentication\cb1 \
\cb3 - `useQuery(['/api/bookings'])` - All bookings with filtering\cb1 \
\cb3 - `useQuery(['/api/athletes'])` - All athlete profiles\cb1 \
\cb3 - `useQuery(['/api/blog-posts'])` - Content management\cb1 \
\cb3 - `useQuery(['/api/tips'])` - Tips management\cb1 \
\cb3 - `useQuery(['/api/availability'])` - Schedule management\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **8 Admin Tabs:**\cb1 \
\cb3 1. **Bookings**: Full CRUD with status updates, filtering, quick actions\cb1 \
\cb3 2. **Upcoming Sessions**: Next 7 days with attendance marking\cb1 \
\cb3 3. **Athletes**: Profile management with birthday tracking\cb1 \
\cb3 4. **Content**: Blog and tips management with rich text editing\cb1 \
\cb3 5. **Schedule**: Weekly availability and exception management\cb1 \
\cb3 6. **Parent Communication**: UI-only message threads (no backend)\cb1 \
\cb3 7. **Payments**: Stripe integration with revenue tracking\cb1 \
\cb3 8. **Analytics**: Booking trends and conversion metrics\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Component Architecture\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### BookingWizard System\cb1 \
\cb3 **Flow Types:**\cb1 \
\cb3 - `new-user`: 8 steps for first-time parents\cb1 \
\cb3 - `athlete-modal`: 8 steps for existing parents with athlete selection\cb1 \
\cb3 - `parent-portal`: 8 steps for logged-in parents\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Step Components:**\cb1 \
\cb3 1. **LessonTypeStep**: Adventure-themed lesson selection\cb1 \
\cb3 2. **AthleteSelectStep**: Existing athlete selection or new athlete form\cb1 \
\cb3 3. **FocusAreasStep**: Apparatus-specific skill selection\cb1 \
\cb3 4. **ScheduleStep**: Available time slot selection\cb1 \
\cb3 5. **ParentInfoStep**: Contact and emergency information\cb1 \
\cb3 6. **SafetyStep**: Pickup/dropoff authorization\cb1 \
\cb3 7. **WaiverStep**: Digital waiver completion\cb1 \
\cb3 8. **PaymentStep**: Stripe checkout integration\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### State Management\cb1 \
\cb3 **BookingFlowContext**: Manages booking wizard state and navigation\cb1 \
\cb3 **TanStack Query Config**: Intelligent caching with different stale times:\cb1 \
\cb3 - Default: 5 minutes\cb1 \
\cb3 - Content: 15 minutes\cb1 \
\cb3 - Stripe products: 1 hour\cb1 \
\cb3 - Authentication: 30 seconds\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Performance Optimizations\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Lazy Loading**: All page components loaded on demand\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Image Optimization**: Intersection observer for lazy image loading\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Prefetching**: Hover prefetching on navigation links\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Caching**: Aggressive caching with React Query\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Bundle Splitting**: Vite automatic code splitting\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ---\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ## 3. BOOKING WIZARD \'97 12-STEP FLOW\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Flow Configuration by User Type\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### New User Flow (8 Steps)\cb1 \
\cb3 ```typescript\cb1 \
\cb3 'new-user': [\cb1 \
\cb3   'lessonType',      // Adventure-themed lesson selection\cb1 \
\cb3   'athleteInfoForm', // New athlete details with photo upload\cb1 \
\cb3   'focusAreas',      // Apparatus-specific skill selection\cb1 \
\cb3   'schedule',        // Available time slot selection\cb1 \
\cb3   'parentInfoForm',  // Parent contact information\cb1 \
\cb3   'safety',          // Pickup/dropoff authorization\cb1 \
\cb3   'waiver',          // Digital waiver completion\cb1 \
\cb3   'payment'          // Stripe checkout session\cb1 \
\cb3 ]\cb1 \
\cb3 ```\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Existing Parent Flow (8 Steps)\cb1 \
\cb3 ```typescript\cb1 \
\cb3 'parent-portal': [\cb1 \
\cb3   'lessonType',      // Lesson type selection\cb1 \
\cb3   'athleteSelect',   // Choose from existing athletes\cb1 \
\cb3   'focusAreas',      // Skill focus areas\cb1 \
\cb3   'schedule',        // Time slot selection\cb1 \
\cb3   'parentConfirm',   // Confirm parent information\cb1 \
\cb3   'safety',          // Safety verification\cb1 \
\cb3   'waiver',          // Waiver completion\cb1 \
\cb3   'payment'          // Payment processing\cb1 \
\cb3 ]\cb1 \
\cb3 ```\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Athlete Modal Flow (8 Steps)\cb1 \
\cb3 ```typescript\cb1 \
\cb3 'athlete-modal': [\cb1 \
\cb3   'lessonType',           // Lesson selection\cb1 \
\cb3   'athleteSelectIfSemi',  // Multi-athlete selection for semi-private\cb1 \
\cb3   'focusAreas',           // Focus area selection\cb1 \
\cb3   'schedule',             // Time slot selection\cb1 \
\cb3   'parentConfirm',        // Parent information confirmation\cb1 \
\cb3   'safety',               // Safety verification\cb1 \
\cb3   'waiver',               // Waiver completion\cb1 \
\cb3   'payment'               // Payment processing\cb1 \
\cb3 ]\cb1 \
\cb3 ```\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Step Details & Data Flow\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Step 1: Lesson Type Selection\cb1 \
\cb3 **Purpose**: Choose adventure-themed lesson type\cb1 \
\cb3 **Fields**: \cb1 \
\cb3 - Quick Journey (30 min individual)\cb1 \
\cb3 - Dual Quest (30 min semi-private)\cb1 \
\cb3 - Deep Dive (60 min individual)\cb1 \
\cb3 - Partner Progression (60 min semi-private)\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Validation**: Required lesson type selection\cb1 \
\cb3 **State**: Stored in BookingFlowContext, not persisted until payment\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Step 2: Athlete Selection/Creation\cb1 \
\cb3 **Purpose**: Identify or create athlete profiles\cb1 \
\cb3 **Fields**: \cb1 \
\cb3 - Existing athletes (dropdown with photos)\cb1 \
\cb3 - New athlete form (name, birthdate, experience, photo)\cb1 \
\cb3 - Semi-private: multiple athlete selection\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Validation**: Athlete information required, age validation\cb1 \
\cb3 **State**: Temporarily stored in context\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Step 3: Focus Areas\cb1 \
\cb3 **Purpose**: Select apparatus-specific training focus\cb1 \
\cb3 **Fields**: \cb1 \
\cb3 - Apparatus selection (Vault, Bars, Beam, Floor, Side Quests)\cb1 \
\cb3 - Skill-specific focus areas per apparatus\cb1 \
\cb3 - Multi-select with visual skill badges\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Validation**: At least one focus area required\cb1 \
\cb3 **State**: Array of focus area IDs in context\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Step 4: Schedule Selection\cb1 \
\cb3 **Purpose**: Choose available time slots\cb1 \
\cb3 **Fields**: \cb1 \
\cb3 - Date picker (blocks past dates)\cb1 \
\cb3 - Time slot dropdown (filtered by availability)\cb1 \
\cb3 - Automatic filtering of booked/blocked times\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Validation**: Future date/time required, availability check\cb1 \
\cb3 **State**: Date and time stored in context\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Step 5: Parent Information\cb1 \
\cb3 **Purpose**: Collect/confirm parent contact details\cb1 \
\cb3 **Fields**: \cb1 \
\cb3 - Parent name, email, phone\cb1 \
\cb3 - Emergency contact information\cb1 \
\cb3 - Pre-filled for existing parents\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Validation**: Required contact information, email format\cb1 \
\cb3 **State**: Parent data in context\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Step 6: Safety Verification\cb1 \
\cb3 **Purpose**: Authorize pickup/dropoff persons\cb1 \
\cb3 **Fields**: \cb1 \
\cb3 - Pickup person name and relationship\cb1 \
\cb3 - Dropoff person name and relationship\cb1 \
\cb3 - Emergency contact authorization\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Validation**: Required safety information\cb1 \
\cb3 **State**: Safety data in context\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Step 7: Waiver Completion\cb1 \
\cb3 **Purpose**: Digital waiver signing\cb1 \
\cb3 **Fields**: \cb1 \
\cb3 - Electronic signature canvas\cb1 \
\cb3 - Waiver text agreement\cb1 \
\cb3 - Date and parent signature\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Validation**: Signature required, agreement checkbox\cb1 \
\cb3 **State**: Waiver data and signature blob\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Step 8: Payment Processing\cb1 \
\cb3 **Purpose**: Stripe checkout session creation\cb1 \
\cb3 **Fields**: \cb1 \
\cb3 - Booking summary display\cb1 \
\cb3 - Payment amount (reservation fee)\cb1 \
\cb3 - Stripe checkout redirect\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Validation**: Payment processing required\cb1 \
\cb3 **Persistence**: All booking data saved to Supabase on successful payment\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Stripe Integration Flow\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Payment Processing\cb1 \
\cb3 1. **Checkout Session Creation**: `/api/stripe/create-checkout-session`\cb1 \
\cb3 2. **Session Data**: Booking details stored in session metadata\cb1 \
\cb3 3. **Redirect**: User redirected to Stripe checkout\cb1 \
\cb3 4. **Webhook**: `checkout.session.completed` creates booking\cb1 \
\cb3 5. **Success Page**: Booking retrieved via `stripe_session_id`\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Payment Flow Details\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Reservation Fee**: Charged upfront via Stripe\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Balance Payment**: Collected at time of lesson\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Refund Policy**: Automated through Stripe API\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Receipt**: Automatic email with booking confirmation\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ---\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ## 4. PARENT PORTAL\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Email-Code Authentication Flow\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Step 1: Email Submission\cb1 \
\cb3 **Endpoint**: `POST /api/parent-auth/send-code`\cb1 \
\cb3 **Process**: \cb1 \
\cb3 1. Parent enters email address\cb1 \
\cb3 2. System generates 6-digit code\cb1 \
\cb3 3. Code sent via Resend email template\cb1 \
\cb3 4. Code stored in database with expiry (15 minutes)\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Step 2: Code Verification\cb1 \
\cb3 **Endpoint**: `POST /api/parent-auth/verify-code`\cb1 \
\cb3 **Process**: \cb1 \
\cb3 1. Parent enters 6-digit code\cb1 \
\cb3 2. Code validated against database\cb1 \
\cb3 3. Session created with secure cookie\cb1 \
\cb3 4. Parent redirected to dashboard\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Step 3: Session Management\cb1 \
\cb3 **Session Config**: \cb1 \
\cb3 - Express-session with secure cookies\cb1 \
\cb3 - Domain: `.coachwilltumbles.com` (production)\cb1 \
\cb3 - Secure: true, sameSite: 'none'\cb1 \
\cb3 - MaxAge: 7 days\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Dashboard Widgets & Features\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Upcoming Sessions Widget\cb1 \
\cb3 **Data Source**: `useQuery(['/api/parent/bookings'])`\cb1 \
\cb3 **Display**: \cb1 \
\cb3 - Next 7 days of confirmed bookings\cb1 \
\cb3 - Session date, time, and athlete\cb1 \
\cb3 - Quick actions: reschedule, cancel, update focus areas\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Athlete Management Widget\cb1 \
\cb3 **Data Source**: `useQuery(['/api/parent/athletes'])`\cb1 \
\cb3 **Features**: \cb1 \
\cb3 - Athlete profiles with photos\cb1 \
\cb3 - Birthday tracking with notifications\cb1 \
\cb3 - Age calculation and experience tracking\cb1 \
\cb3 - Edit modal with form validation\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Booking History Widget\cb1 \
\cb3 **Data Source**: `useQuery(['/api/parent/bookings'])`\cb1 \
\cb3 **Features**: \cb1 \
\cb3 - Sortable booking history\cb1 \
\cb3 - Status filtering (confirmed, completed, cancelled)\cb1 \
\cb3 - Payment status tracking\cb1 \
\cb3 - Reschedule functionality\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Waiver Status Widget\cb1 \
\cb3 **Data Source**: Embedded in booking queries\cb1 \
\cb3 **Features**: \cb1 \
\cb3 - Waiver completion status per athlete\cb1 \
\cb3 - Digital waiver completion links\cb1 \
\cb3 - Waiver archive access\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### CRUD Rules & Permissions\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Parents Can Edit:\cb1 \
\cb3 - Their own profile information\cb1 \
\cb3 - Emergency contact details\cb1 \
\cb3 - Athlete profiles (name, birthdate, experience)\cb1 \
\cb3 - Focus areas for future bookings\cb1 \
\cb3 - Booking preferences\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Parents Cannot Edit:\cb1 \
\cb3 - Completed booking details\cb1 \
\cb3 - Payment information\cb1 \
\cb3 - Session attendance records\cb1 \
\cb3 - Other parents' data\cb1 \
\cb3 - Admin-only fields\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Session Restrictions:\cb1 \
\cb3 - Cannot reschedule less than 24 hours before session\cb1 \
\cb3 - Cannot cancel without fees less than 4 hours before\cb1 \
\cb3 - Cannot edit athlete information during active booking\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Logout & Session Expiry\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Manual Logout:\cb1 \
\cb3 **Endpoint**: `POST /api/parent-auth/logout`\cb1 \
\cb3 **Process**: Session destroyed, cookies cleared, redirect to login\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Automatic Expiry:\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Session Duration**: 7 days maximum\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Inactivity**: 24 hours of inactivity\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Token Refresh**: Automatic on page load if session valid\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ---\cb1 \
