\cb3 ## 7. EMAIL AUTOMATION (Resend)\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Email Template System\cb1 \
\
\cb3 | Template | Trigger Event | Data Injected | Recipient | Logged |\cb1 \
\cb3 |----------|---------------|---------------|-----------|--------|\cb1 \
\cb3 | Welcome | First parent login | `\{parentName\}` | Parent | \uc0\u9989  |\cb1 \
\cb3 | Booking Confirmation | Stripe `checkout.session.completed` | `\{parentName, sessionDate, athleteName, lessonType\}` | Parent | \uc0\u9989  |\cb1 \
\cb3 | Booking Cancellation | Booking cancelled | `\{parentName, sessionDate, athleteName, reason\}` | Parent | \uc0\u9989  |\cb1 \
\cb3 | Reschedule Confirmation | Booking rescheduled | `\{parentName, oldDate, newDate, athleteName\}` | Parent | \uc0\u9989  |\cb1 \
\cb3 | Waiver Reminder | Booking without waiver after 12h | `\{parentName, athleteName, waiverLink\}` | Parent | \uc0\u9989  |\cb1 \
\cb3 | Session Reminder | 24h before session | `\{parentName, athleteName, sessionDate, focusAreas\}` | Parent | \uc0\u9989  |\cb1 \
\cb3 | Training Follow-Up | 2h after session | `\{parentName, athleteName, sessionDate, feedback\}` | Parent | \uc0\u9989  |\cb1 \
\cb3 | Birthday Celebration | Daily cron at 09:00 | `\{parentName, athleteName, birthdayDate\}` | Parent | \uc0\u9989  |\cb1 \
\cb3 | New Content Alert | Blog/tip published | `\{parentName, contentTitle, contentLink, contentType\}` | All opted-in parents | \uc0\u9989  |\cb1 \
\cb3 | Payment Reminder | Payment failed | `\{parentName, athleteName, sessionDate, paymentLink\}` | Parent | \uc0\u9989  |\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Email Template Structure\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Template Components\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Header**: Adventure-themed branding with logo\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Content**: Personalized message with dynamic data\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Footer**: Contact information and unsubscribe link\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Styling**: Consistent with website theme\cb1 \
\
\cb3 #### Template Examples\cb1 \
\
\cb3 **Booking Confirmation Template**\cb1 \
\cb3 ```typescript\cb1 \
\cb3 export const BookingConfirmationEmail = (\{\cb1 \
\cb3   parentName,\cb1 \
\cb3   athleteName,\cb1 \
\cb3   sessionDate,\cb1 \
\cb3   sessionTime,\cb1 \
\cb3   lessonType,\cb1 \
\cb3   focusAreas\cb1 \
\cb3 \}: BookingConfirmationProps) => (\cb1 \
\cb3   <Html>\cb1 \
\cb3     <Head />\cb1 \
\cb3     <Body>\cb1 \
\cb3       <Container>\cb1 \
\cb3         <Heading>Your Adventure Awaits! \uc0\u55356 \u57258 </Heading>\cb1 \
\cb3         <Text>Hi \{parentName\},</Text>\cb1 \
\cb3         <Text>\cb1 \
\cb3           Great news! \{athleteName\}'s \{lessonType\} session is confirmed for \{sessionDate\} at \{sessionTime\}.\cb1 \
\cb3         </Text>\cb1 \
\cb3         <Text>Focus Areas: \{focusAreas.join(', ')\}</Text>\cb1 \
\cb3         <Button href=\{`$\{process.env.FRONTEND_URL\}/parent-dashboard`\}>\cb1 \
