\cb3 ## Best Practices & Recommendations\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Security Considerations\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Input Validation**: All user inputs validated with Zod\cb1 \
\cb3 - **SQL Injection Prevention**: Parameterized queries only\cb1 \
\cb3 - **XSS Protection**: React automatic escaping\cb1 \
\cb3 - **CSRF Protection**: Session-based authentication\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Rate Limiting**: Implement for auth endpoints\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Secure Headers**: Add security headers middleware\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Performance Optimization\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Database Indexing**: Index frequently queried columns\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Query Optimization**: Use joins instead of N+1 queries\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Caching**: Implement Redis for session storage\cb1 \
\cb3 - **CDN**: Use CDN for static assets\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Image Optimization**: Compress and resize images\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Bundle Splitting**: Lazy load non-critical code\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Monitoring & Logging\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Error Tracking**: Implement Sentry or similar\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Performance Monitoring**: Track response times\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Business Metrics**: Monitor booking conversion rates\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Uptime Monitoring**: External uptime checks\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Log Aggregation**: Centralized logging system\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Backup Strategy\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Database Backups**: Daily automated backups\cb1 \
\cb3 - **File Storage**: Backup uploaded images\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Configuration**: Backup environment variables\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Code Repository**: Multiple repository mirrors\cb1 \
\cb3 - **Disaster Recovery**: Documented recovery procedures\cb1 \
